body:
The following query filter finds all documents where the value of
`name` is "Andrea Le":

```shell
{ name: "Andrea Le" }
```

The query returns the following document:

```JSON
{
   "_id": { "$oid": "5e349915cebae490877d561d" },
   "name": "Andrea Le",
   "email": "andrea_le@fake-mail.com",
   "school": {
      "name": "Northwestern"
   },
   "version": 5,
   "scores": [ 85, 95, 75 ],
   "dateCreated": { "$date": "2003-03-26" }
}
```
